        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GAE for memoir on earthworms [<hi rend="italic">Bidrag till Skandinaviens Oligochaetfauna</hi> (1871)]. CD by chance is just now observing "one little point in their habits". Will be happy to learn something about the places frequented by the various species.</p> 
